243
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:12,840
I don’t want you to worry about it.

244
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:18,480
So, you didn’t plan

245
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:20,000
to live with me, right?

246
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,080
