247
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:24,960
Haoyue, you wronged me.

248
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:28,120
Your brother is still young

249
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:30,000
and needs nursing.

250
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,720
